headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid CWST and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Casella Waste Systems’s shares (currently trading at $99.29) have posted a disappointing 10.8% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 5.8% gain. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
